Modifications by ForgeGuard include (non-exhaustive): an OpenAI-compatible
FastAPI transcription and translation server with /health and /ready endpoints
and non-blocking background model warmup, optional bearer-token authentication,
a React web console, CUDA cu128 (amd64) and Jetson (arm64/L4T) container images
with models baked in at build time (revision-pinned), a Helm chart, and removal
of the vendored library and bare-metal install path in favor of container-only
distribution. See CHANGELOG.md for details.

This product uses OpenAI Whisper model weights
(https://github.com/openai/whisper), MIT License, as converted to CTranslate2
format by Systran (https://huggingface.co/Systran), served via the
faster-whisper (https://github.com/SYSTRAN/faster-whisper) and CTranslate2
(https://github.com/OpenNMT/CTranslate2) libraries, both licensed under the
MIT License.
